    {
      "id": "PopularPost268573",
      "post_content": "People who think this card is crap greatly underestimates its use. there are dozens of one and two cost instant cards out there that can stall people or just stop them in their tracks: [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog)/[Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) are great against heavy creature decks. [Counterspell](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Counterspell) just to stop anything and everything being played and there are dozens of others to choose from.  \n  \nAnd not to mention being able to get this out turn two possibly one if your lucky and you have a good start to keeping your opponent at bay for a while. yes there are ways to get rid of it but if you get it out early your usually good to go.",
